 First, we need to find the total time spent on meditation and yoga practice in 5 days. Since she meditates for 15 minutes and yoga for 1 hour, the total time spent in 5 days is \text{Total time} = 15 \text{ minutes/day} \times 5 \text{ days} + 1 \text{ hour/day} \times 5 \text{ days} 
